# =====================================================================
# .vercelignore — files Vercel should NEVER deploy to holisticunity.app.
#
# Ranges from "would expose secrets" (P0) to "just clutter".
# When in doubt: prefer ignoring. Anything truly public must live under
# explicit subdirs (/blog/, /images/, root-level *.html, shared.css, etc.).
# =====================================================================

# Internal documentation — describes our infrastructure, would help a
# scraper map our stack and find more attack surface.
CLAUDE.md
AGENTS.md
README.md
docs/

# Editorial drafts — pre-publication markdown. Indexable by Google if
# served, would compete with the real published articles for SEO.
blog/_drafts/
blog/_*.py

# Generator scripts — historically have been the source of P0 leaks
# (FAL_KEY hardcoded fallbacks). They have ZERO reason to be public,
# regardless of whether they currently contain secrets.
images/blog/_*.py
images/blog/_*.sh
scripts/*.py

# Preview / staging mirrors — these are local-only iteration spaces.
# Originally this excluded the whole `preview-redesign/` and
# `preview-live-style/` directories. That broke the production homepage
# in 2026-05-08: index.html references images from those folders
# (e.g. `preview-redesign/images/hero-v4-session.jpg`, hu-theta.jpg, …)
# and a CLI deploy honoured the wholesale ignore, leaving 18 broken
# <img> tags on the live homepage.
#
# The original intent was "no staging HTML pages or generator scripts
# on the public domain", not "no images". So we now exclude only the
# things that genuinely need to be hidden — HTML pages and generator
# scripts (the P0 leak source) — and let image assets ride along.
# Subdirectory excludes use `**/*.py` so scripts at any depth (e.g.
# `preview-redesign/images/_gen_hero_hu.py`) stay out.
preview-redesign/*.html
preview-redesign/**/*.py
preview-redesign/**/*.sh
preview-live-style/*.html
preview-live-style/**/*.py
preview-live-style/**/*.sh

# Dated backups left in the repo from manual edits.
*.backup-*
*.bak
*.orig

# OS / editor cruft.
.DS_Store
.playwright-cli/
output/
.claude/

# Misterious one-off file (unverified content fingerprint?). Excluded
# by default; if it turns out to be needed, it can be re-added explicitly.
1e88c1c8a5c297b7219332e0ab88e974236f0d2cb9974f1f48646d072ff3aeb4.txt
